!**/src/test/**/out/

### Spring Tool Suite (STS) ###
.apt_generated/
.classpath
.factorypath
.project
.settings/
.springBeans
.sts4-cache/
bin/
!**/src/main/**/bin/
!**/src/test/**/bin/

### NetBeans ###
/nbproject/private/
/nbbuild/
/dist/
/nbdist/
/.nb-gradle/

### VS Code ###
.vscode/

